    body
        .container.mt-5
            h1 Privacy Policy
            p Last Updated: [Insert Date]
            p Welcome to [Your Website Name]! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website.

            h2 Information We Collect
            h3 Username and Email Address
            p
                strong When Collected:
                |  We only collect your username and email address when you register for an account on our website.
            p
                strong Purpose:
                |  This information is used to enable you to add builds and post comments on the website.

            h2 Account Creation
            p
                strong Optional Registration:
                |  You are not required to create an account to browse and use our website. Registration is entirely optional and only necessary if you wish to contribute content (such as builds and comments).

            h2 Cookies
            p
                strong Login Cookie:
                |  We use a single cookie to manage user login sessions. This cookie is essential for allowing you to stay logged in while you navigate our website.
            p
                strong No Tracking Cookies:
                |  We do not use any tracking cookies on our website.
            p
                strong No Advertising Cookies:
                |  Our website does not display ads, and therefore, no advertising cookies are used.

            h2 How We Use Your Information
            p
                strong User Contributions:
                |  Your username and email address are used to attribute builds and comments to you.
            p
                strong Communication:
                |  We may use your email address to communicate with you regarding your account or any issues related to your contributions.

            h2 Data Protection
            p We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. To prevent unauthorized access or disclosure, we have put in place suitable physical, electronic, and managerial procedures to safeguard and secure the information we collect online.

            h2 Sharing of Information
            p We do not share, sell, or distribute your personal information to third parties unless required by law.

            h2 Your Rights
            p
                strong Access:
                |  You have the right to access the personal information we hold about you.
            p
                strong Correction:
                |  You have the right to correct any inaccuracies in the information we hold about you.
            p
                strong Deletion:
                |  You have the right to request the deletion of your personal information.

            h2 Changes to This Privacy Policy
            p We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

            h2 Contact Us
            p If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].

            p Thank you for using [Your Website Name]. We are committed to protecting your privacy and providing a safe online experience.

